Kenyan songstress Avril Nyambura has come out to explain her decision to keep her pregnancy a top secret. The singer only recently shared the first picture of her baby bump to confirm the pregnancy rumors. She however did not disclose her due date. Nairobi News has confirmed that Avril is currently on her third trimester. In an Instagram post on Tuesday, Avril explained that she wanted better control in managing the news about the pregnancy. "It was going to be in my time, my terms never anyone else... " she posted. Avril has for long been rumoured to be in a relation with music video director J Blessing. The two are said to be madly in love. J Blessing reportedly gifted Avril BMW 3 Series worth Sh3.5 million to ease her travel around the city. Avril has been spotted a couple of timeS driving the car in the city.